lan a terrorist attack in the German capital, Berlin. According to the ruling by the Berlin Regional Court, the Gesundbrunnen Shopping Centre has been considered as a target, but the militants… January 24, 2020 In "Foreign" Belgian investigators are gradually piecing together how three men staged three attacks in Brussels, killing 31 people and wounding 270 others, while a fourth assailant fled. March 24, 2016 In "News" Kao Xiong, a California man has pleaded guilty to sending more than 150 threatening or hoax letters in 2017 to President Donald Trump and to former presidents, FBI offices and other individuals and businesses. January 5, 2019 In "News"